{"type":"message","id":"2a8aa698","parentId":"d31cfab7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:18:43.917Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2p9w26jaxp1z_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4915\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2873\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master 242aa67] pulse: 2026-03-24 111816\n 6 files changed, 371 insertions(+), 75 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 111816.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 111816.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 111714.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 111816 - CFI analysis revealed that 44.8% of invariants are pure noise (CFI=0) and only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7). The next step is to validate whether CFI-weighted compression outperforms frequency-only baseline for next-pulse prediction.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"young-pine","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4915\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2873\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master 242aa67] pulse: 2026-03-24 111816\n 6 files changed, 371 insertions(+), 75 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 111816.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 111816.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 111714.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 111816 - CFI analysis revealed that 44.8% of invariants are pure noise (CFI=0) and only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7). The next step is to validate whether CFI-weighted compression outperforms frequency-only baseline for next-pulse prediction.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774365523913}}
